data.description: Introducing 6228 old Kingston nestled within the esteemed Cambridge meadows neighborhood. Minutes from I-20, the Atlanta airport, Sweetwater creek state park, and other parks and recreational areas. This exquisite residence spans 3,600 square feet, offering a spacious and comfortable living experience. The seller spared no expense adding tons of upgrades throughout. This Apple Smart home provides ample space for a growing family or room for guests. upon entering, you'll be captivated by the open concept design on the main floor, with hardwood floors. The large open kitchen is equipped with tons of storage, a spacious island, custom built ins in the pantry, a gas cooktop, double wall ovens, new upgraded cabinetry with built in wine storage. Upstairs you're greeted with hardwood floors, 4 bedrooms, including a bonus room/home office, and 2 full bathrooms. The oversized primary suite has a cozy built-in fireplace perfect for those cold winter nights. Step into the primary bathroom that exudes a spa-like ambiance, featuring a double vanity, large soaking tub, separate shower, and a custom walk-in closet. Don't miss the opportunity to own this remarkable home, where comfort meets style, and accessibility!
